OL,3,CUniversities awarded funding to help
OL,4,Crecruit 'world's top researchers' to UK
OL,6,FA group of leading universities and
OL,7,Fresearch organisations has been
OL,8,Fselected to deliver a #54 million
OL,9,FGovernment fund to recruit world-
OL,10,Fleading researchers to the UK.
OL,12,FThe Global Talent Fund, administered
OL,13,Fby UK Research and Innovation (UKRI),
OL,14,Faims to attract up to 80 researchers
OL,15,Fin high-priority sectors such as life
OL,16,Fsciences and digital technologies.
