OL,3,CUniversities awarded funding to help
OL,4,Crecruit 'world's top researchers' to UK
OL,6,FThe institutions selected are:
OL,7,FUniversity of Bath; Queen's University
OL,8,FBelfast; University of Birmingham;
OL,9,FUniversity of Cambridge; Cardiff
OL,10,FUniversity; Imperial College London;
OL,11,FUniversity of Oxford; University of
OL,12,FSouthampton; University of
OL,13,FStrathclyde; University of Warwick;
OL,14,FJohn Innes Centreand MRC Laboratory
OL,15,Fof Molecular Biology.
OL,17,FThe five-year Government fund, which
OL,18,Fstarts in 2025/26, will cover all
OL,19,Feligible costs with no requirement for
OL,20,Fmatch funding from research
OL,21,Forganisations.
