OL,4,Crecruit 'world's top researchers' to UK
OL,6,FVisa and relocation costs for
OL,7,Fresearchers and their family members
OL,8,Fwill be covered by the fund.
OL,10,FScience minister Lord Vallance said:
OL,11,F"Genius is not bound by geography. But
OL,12,Fthe UK is one of the few places
OL,13,Fblessed with the infrastructure,
OL,14,Fskills base, world-class institutions
OL,15,Fand international ties needed to
OL,16,Fincubate brilliant ideas, and turn
OL,17,Fthem into new medicines that save
OL,18,Flives, new products that make our
OL,19,Flives easier, and even entirely new
OL,20,Fjobs and industries.
