OL,3,CUniversities awarded funding to help
OL,4,Crecruit 'world's top researchers' to UK
OL,6,F"Bringing these innovations to life,
OL,7,Fhere in Britain, will be critical to
OL,8,Fdelivering this Government's Plan For
OL,9,FChange.
OL,11,F"My message to the bold and the brave
OL,12,Fwho are advancing new ideas, wherever
OL,13,Fthey are, is: our doors are open to
OL,14,Fyou.
OL,16,F"We want to work with you, support
OL,17,Fyou, and give you a home where you can
OL,18,Fmake your ideas a reality we all
OL,19,Fbenefit from."
