OL,6,FChancellor Rachel Reeves said: "The UK
OL,7,Fis home to some of the world's best
OL,8,Funiversities which are vital for
OL,9,Fattracting international top talent.
OL,11,F"Supported by our new Global Talent
OL,12,FTaskforce, the Global Talent Fund will
OL,13,Fcement our position as a leading
OL,14,Fchoice for the world's top researchers
OL,15,Fto make their home here, supercharging
OL,16,Fgrowth and delivering on our Plan For
OL,17,FChange."
